---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Drunk Robot - About">
  <div class="about">
    <h1 class="display">About Drunk Robot</h1>
    <p>
      Drunk Robot was a weekly webcomic that ran from 2011 to 2016, written by
      Brian Powell and drawn by Jeff Pina. A new strip landed every Monday,
      skewering comics, sci-fi, and nerd culture at large.
    </p>
    <p>
      The original site went offline years ago. This archive was restored from
      snapshots preserved by the
      <a href="https://web.archive.org">Internet Archive's Wayback Machine</a>,
      and rebuilt as a fast, modern site. Some strips may be lost to time; what
      could be recovered lives in the <a href="/archive/">archive</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about { max-width: 640px; }
  h1 { margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem; font-size: 1.8rem; }
</style>
